name: Poisoned
description: This work examines the public's response to all the information it obtains, without criticizing it before it is factually believed. These preferences make people take a passive attitude, because they don't consider something before responding to it. Therefore, people hyperbole as if swallowing whatever is in front of the mouth, although some of it is vomited back up. There are times when there is valid information, on the other hand it is not uncommon for there to be erroneous information. For this reason, it is hoped that each person's awareness will arise so that they are not in a hurry to label something or really. In other words, trying to review what he got.
